## Short Centered Breaks

Partial-width rules centered on the page:

```css
:root {
  --thematic-break-width: 30%;
  --thematic-break-margin-left: auto;
  --thematic-break-margin-right: auto;
  --thematic-break-border-width: 1px;
}
```

